                Get started in minutes with a simple example. Install the package and start building immediately.
            </BitText>
            <br />
            <BitText Typography="BitTypography.H6" Gutter>1. Install the package</BitText>
            <CodeBox>dotnet add package Bit.BlazorUI</CodeBox>
            <br />
            <BitText Typography="BitTypography.H6" Gutter>2. Add styles and scripts</BitText>
            <CodeBox Language="html">&lt;link href="_content/Bit.BlazorUI/styles/bit.blazorui.css" rel="stylesheet" />
&lt;script src="_content/Bit.BlazorUI/scripts/bit.blazorui.js">&lt;/script></CodeBox>
            <br />
            <BitText Typography="BitTypography.H6" Gutter>3. Add to your Blazor components</BitText>
